```plantuml
@startuml gaiax_fLibra
actor User
participant "Nuxt.js Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Vuex Store" as Vuex
participant "Firebase/Firestore" as Firestore
participant "Ethereum Smart Contract" as Ethereum
participant "Libra Blockchain" as Libra
participant "Elasticsearch" as Elasticsearch
participant "IPFS" as IPFS

User -> Frontend: Browse Marketplace
Frontend -> Elasticsearch: Search Items (keyword/category)
Elasticsearch --> Frontend: Return Search Results
Frontend -> Firestore: Fetch Item Details
Firestore --> Frontend: Return Item Data
Frontend -> IPFS: Load Item Images
IPFS --> Frontend: Return Images

User -> Frontend: Post New Item
Frontend -> IPFS: Upload Item Images
IPFS --> Frontend: Return Image Hash
Frontend -> Firestore: Save Item Details
Firestore -> Elasticsearch: Index New Item (via listener)
Frontend -> Ethereum: Register Item (via smart contract)
Ethereum --> Frontend: Confirmation

User -> Frontend: Purchase Item
Frontend -> Ethereum: Initiate Purchase (escrow)
Ethereum --> Frontend: Confirmation
Frontend -> Libra: Transfer Payment
Libra --> Frontend: Transaction Receipt
Ethereum -> Firestore: Update Item Status (sold)
Firestore -> Elasticsearch: Update Index (via listener)

User -> Frontend: Mark Item as Delivered
Frontend -> Ethereum: Confirm Delivery
Ethereum -> Libra: Release Funds to Seller
Ethereum -> Firestore: Update Delivery Status
Firestore -> Elasticsearch: Update Index (via listener)

User -> Frontend: Leave Review
Frontend -> Firestore: Save Review Data
Firestore -> Elasticsearch: Update Index (via listener)
Frontend -> Ethereum: Record Review (optional)
@enduml
```